{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2015/10/19/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Hexo - 版本控制與發佈到 GitHub","date":"19 October 2015","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Node.js","Hexo","GitHub"],"coverImage":null},"id":"6b8a94c4-9185-5d49-a7de-1fbf07cad6f0","html":"<h2>前言</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://skychang.github.io/2015/10/06/Install-Hexo/\">上一篇</a>我們看到了怎樣安裝 Hexo，並且了解如何將現有的文章轉入進來，接下來，我們就來看看，如何將原始檔 ( Markdown ) 放到 GitHub 進行版控，並且!!把編譯過 ( 將 Markdown 透過 Hexo 轉成 HTML ) 的 HTML 放到 GitHub 上。</p>\n<h2>使用 GitHub 當作 Blogger</h2>\n<p>目前 GitHub 有支援個人與專案，一個帳號，可以建立一個個人網站和多個專案網站。詳細可以參考底下兩篇。\n<a href=\"http://skychang.github.io/2014/07/31/GitHub-GitHub-Page-for-User/\">個人</a>\n<a href=\"http://skychang.github.io/2014/07/31/GitHub-GitHub-Page-for-Project/\">專案</a></p>\n<h2>為什麼要備份 Source 到 GitHub</h2>\n<p>現在是版控的時代了，除了程式碼要版控之外，圖檔要版控，甚至連虛擬機都要版控 ( Docker ) ，那文章勒，文章其實也可以版控，但我們版控的不是 HTML ，而是 Markdown，Markdown 就猶如我們的 Source Code，而 HTML 就如同是編譯過執行程式。</p>\n<p>既然我們選擇使用 GitHub , 那自然就使用 GitHub 進行版控吧!</p>\n<p>( 當然，別忘了先在 GitHub 上開個 Repo 阿!! , 也別忘了要先安裝 git 應用程式喔!! )</p>\n<h2>git 初始化與設定</h2>\n<p>首先，大家非常不陌生的 <code class=\"language-text\">git init</code> ，初始化一下。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git init</code></pre></div>\n<p>透過 git init 我們就可以針對此目錄下進行版控。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/1d5a8/14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAMCAYAAABiDJ37AAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAfElEQVQoz+2OwQ6CMBBEt7b9MQ+oIbH4aSZwxC0maO2Jq/HjhkJ6lZT02sM7bDLzdujedmA74GEtembw8ITzHu7j8Xq7JMYAh+70/YGU1hCCAgJElMXxUoOElH8Dy5MUlFJrvroa0CEeOcg46tzcthfuFpoiLMLdwpNpMAOu5SCKJFG+DQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"14\"\n        title=\"14\"\n        src=\"/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/78d47/14.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/56d15/14.png 200w,\n/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/d9f49/14.png 400w,\n/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/78d47/14.png 800w,\n/static/f16395b0ab1a515d9536f09a993ea26d/1d5a8/14.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，我們就可以透過底下指令，加入遠端的位置，到時候我們就可以 sync 上去。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git remote add origin git@github.com:帳號/Repo</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/1d5a8/15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"15\"\n        title=\"15\"\n        src=\"/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/78d47/15.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/56d15/15.png 200w,\n/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/d9f49/15.png 400w,\n/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/78d47/15.png 800w,\n/static/03aa2ad13814d2ec6ac0d107998fd4c4/1d5a8/15.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>當然，如果這樣就成功了，就不會有這篇了，如果此時你直接下 git push ，那會出現權限不足的問題，而這邊，我們透過產生金鑰的方式，這樣就不用每次都需要 key 帳號密碼。</p>\n<p>我們先到 .ssh 的目錄底下去，原則上，看到的應該是空的 ( 只會有 known<em>hosts ) ，如果有看到 id</em>rsa.pub 也可以直接拿來用，如果沒看到，我們就來產生一個吧!!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 786px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1f8371a4fa226d4a165db025714e81e7/d703b/16.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"16\"\n        title=\"16\"\n        src=\"/static/1f8371a4fa226d4a165db025714e81e7/d703b/16.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f8371a4fa226d4a165db025714e81e7/56d15/16.png 200w,\n/static/1f8371a4fa226d4a165db025714e81e7/d9f49/16.png 400w,\n/static/1f8371a4fa226d4a165db025714e81e7/d703b/16.png 786w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我們可以到 program Files\\Git\\usr\\bin 目錄底下，下這個指令，透過這個指令，就可以幫我們產生金鑰。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的Email&quot;</code></pre></div>\n<p>預設金鑰就會產生到 .ssh 底下去。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/1d5a8/17.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"17\"\n        title=\"17\"\n        src=\"/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/78d47/17.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/56d15/17.png 200w,\n/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/d9f49/17.png 400w,\n/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/78d47/17.png 800w,\n/static/079397fa97c2536310f38fbaa8df0db8/1d5a8/17.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如下圖，我們就可以看到 id<em>rsa 和 id</em>rsa.pub 這兩個檔案嚕!!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 786px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f712ff5fe7ce9d020f5c0c9ac4ee752/d703b/18.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"18\"\n        title=\"18\"\n        src=\"/static/6f712ff5fe7ce9d020f5c0c9ac4ee752/d703b/18.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f712ff5fe7ce9d020f5c0c9ac4ee752/56d15/18.png 200w,\n/static/6f712ff5fe7ce9d020f5c0c9ac4ee752/d9f49/18.png 400w,\n/static/6f712ff5fe7ce9d020f5c0c9ac4ee752/d703b/18.png 786w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，我們打開 id.rsa.pub ( 用記事本開啟 )，我們把底下的金鑰 copy 下來。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/cda85/19.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"19\"\n        title=\"19\"\n        src=\"/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/78d47/19.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/56d15/19.png 200w,\n/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/d9f49/19.png 400w,\n/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/78d47/19.png 800w,\n/static/a94d51485fd873e1a31e37c2e9773c49/cda85/19.png 928w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>然後貼到 GitHub 上去。\n( 注意，GitHub 可以針對 專案 進行金鑰的設定，如下圖，或是整個帳號，如下下圖，你可以決定你的金鑰的範圍，但是一組金鑰，只能出現在 GitHub 的這個帳號底下一次，也就是說，如果你把金鑰拿去設定 專案 ，那你就不能用同樣的金鑰設定在其他的專案上了 )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/3b5a6/20.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20\"\n        title=\"20\"\n        src=\"/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/78d47/20.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/56d15/20.png 200w,\n/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/d9f49/20.png 400w,\n/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/78d47/20.png 800w,\n/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/64756/20.png 1200w,\n/static/22ea6939a354f279a6eca7cf20a2db6d/3b5a6/20.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果要設定給完整帳號，我們可以從帳號設定的底下進行金鑰的貼上，貼上後，就可以了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/3b5a6/21.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"21\"\n        title=\"21\"\n        src=\"/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/78d47/21.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/56d15/21.png 200w,\n/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/d9f49/21.png 400w,\n/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/78d47/21.png 800w,\n/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/64756/21.png 1200w,\n/static/4bee61aaaa8298f4c7e730ca9fbb3e6b/3b5a6/21.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>推送到 GitHub</h2>\n<p>接下來，就是大家熟悉的指令了....</p>\n<p>首先，把網站的 source 全部加入.... ( 這邊不用擔心編譯過後的 HTML 也被加入進去，當我們使用 Hexo init 的時候，預設就會把 public 這個含有 HTML 的目錄給過濾掉了。 )</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git add .</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/1d5a8/22.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAMCAYAAABiDJ37AAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAhElEQVQoz+2SvQ6CMBRGb7nlzQxBFPl5N2JYaElMaXVycuDhPijOJk3owOBwti/nnuFSd++hxxGD0hsPY+CeL1jnYKyFmcJQSuH9mUEsUwhBKwJEtItTfgWJhH8O/JEQ5Brl90XVghKWu8uYv1F5WXshRxNmlyqu8HxrIgvLv/BwQv+HCx1NIKV2nb/BAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"22\"\n        title=\"22\"\n        src=\"/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/78d47/22.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/56d15/22.png 200w,\n/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/d9f49/22.png 400w,\n/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/78d47/22.png 800w,\n/static/888b2f366a1bb8ab1d02b6335d57ecf0/1d5a8/22.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>然後，簽入到本機。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git commit -m &quot;First&quot;</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/1d5a8/23.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAMCAYAAABiDJ37AAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAhElEQVQoz+2SOw6DMBBE16y5GYog4RNytwjRxFBgMFRUKXK4wYYeClxQpHjaZvRmiqV3VaNpW3xUs9JpDTNOGMxoMevV/XCIUgrz9wdiGUIIsggQ0SmiOAWJgA+DrmwPaUe53L14gQKWp5cxb6Pi7OmE7E14exR+hUleehZmf+HlhO4PFzcyIKvqZ7AYAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"23\"\n        title=\"23\"\n        src=\"/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/78d47/23.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/56d15/23.png 200w,\n/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/d9f49/23.png 400w,\n/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/78d47/23.png 800w,\n/static/86a55b92286c4d7749e72118bcb988cc/1d5a8/23.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>推送到 GitHub。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git push origin master</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/1d5a8/24.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"24\"\n        title=\"24\"\n        src=\"/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/78d47/24.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/56d15/24.png 200w,\n/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/d9f49/24.png 400w,\n/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/78d47/24.png 800w,\n/static/7ae3a19f4e84f341b3c572b850bb5211/1d5a8/24.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>到這邊，我們 source 就可以安心地放到 GitHub 進行版控嚕....</p>\n<h2>進行佈署</h2>\n<p>在開始前，我們要先裝 hexo-deployer-git ，透過這個套件，才能佈署到 GitHub 上。\n我們可以到我們的 hexo 目錄底下，透過底下指令進行安裝。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>接著，我們要開始進行佈署，首先，我們要修改 _config.yml 這個檔案，如下圖。\n這邊表示我們要使用 git ，並且設定遠端的 repo。\n如果有分支需求的朋友，可以參考<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/deployment.html\">官網</a>的設定，官網也有許多 FTP 等地佈署方式。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 606px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1c025c470ac347b78b3e3793fe650677/cec09/25.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"25\"\n        title=\"25\"\n        src=\"/static/1c025c470ac347b78b3e3793fe650677/cec09/25.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1c025c470ac347b78b3e3793fe650677/56d15/25.png 200w,\n/static/1c025c470ac347b78b3e3793fe650677/d9f49/25.png 400w,\n/static/1c025c470ac347b78b3e3793fe650677/cec09/25.png 606w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>然後，我們要先把我們的 Markdown 編譯成 HTML。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">hexo g</code></pre></div>\n<p>接著，我們只要下底下指令即可，hexo 就會自動的把 HTML 佈署到 github 上了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">hexo deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 418px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b537a01d3b4fe9b6f16b6539b52a54bd/2bbac/26.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"26\"\n        title=\"26\"\n        src=\"/static/b537a01d3b4fe9b6f16b6539b52a54bd/2bbac/26.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b537a01d3b4fe9b6f16b6539b52a54bd/56d15/26.png 200w,\n/static/b537a01d3b4fe9b6f16b6539b52a54bd/d9f49/26.png 400w,\n/static/b537a01d3b4fe9b6f16b6539b52a54bd/2bbac/26.png 418w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 418px) 100vw, 418px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>完工!!</p>\n<h2>等等，新文章哩!!?</h2>\n<p>是低，下一篇，我們即將針對新文章的撰寫，來和大家講一些小技巧。</p>\n<h2>參考資料</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://serverfault.com/questions/78048/whats-the-difference-between-ip-address-0-0-0-0-and-127-0-0-1#comment63540_78049\">http://serverfault.com/questions/78048/whats-the-difference-between-ip-address-0-0-0-0-and-127-0-0-1#comment63540_78049</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/\">http://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next\">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://git-scm.com/book/zh-tw/v1/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84-Git-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-SSH-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%87%91%E9%91%B0\">https://git-scm.com/book/zh-tw/v1/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84-Git-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-SSH-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%87%91%E9%91%B0</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/adamjohnson/5682757\">https://gist.github.com/adamjohnson/5682757</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"前言 上一篇我們看到了怎樣安裝 Hexo，並且了解如何將現有的文章轉入進來，接下來，我們就來看看，如何將原始檔 ( Markdown ) 放到 GitHub 進行版控，並且!!把編譯過 ( 將 Markdown 透過 Hexo 轉成 HTML ) 的 HTML 放到 GitHub…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Hexo - 安裝 Hexo","tags":["Node.js","Hexo","Github"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2015/10/06/Hexo-Install_Hexo/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Hexo-Install_Hexo/Hexo-Install_Hexo.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"使用 fetch 來進行 Ajax 呼叫","tags":["JavaScript"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2015/11/02/JavaScript-Use_Javascript_Fetch/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/blog.sanc.idv.tw/JavaScript-Use_Javascript_Fetch.md"}}}}